<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="sec-header">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Professional Profile</div>
    <h2 class="sec-title">Summary</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="about-layout">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>Finance &amp; Accounts Professional with more than five years of hands-on experience spanning Fintech, Gaming, E-commerce, and Manufacturing industries. My core expertise covers end-to-end Accounts Payable (AP), Accounts Receivable (AR), Procure-to-Pay (P2P), and Treasury operations, complemented by deep competency in GST, TDS, and cross-border statutory compliance.</p>
      <p>I have consistently operated in high-volume transaction environments — reconciling 10,000+ payment gateway line items per cycle, processing 200+ vendor invoices monthly at 99% accuracy, and managing multi-currency treasury accounts across AED, USD, SAR, CAD, EUR, and INR. My work spans both domestic and international financial operations with exposure to SOX control frameworks.</p>
      <p>What differentiates my professional profile is a strong focus on process automation. I have designed and deployed Power Query frameworks and Python tools that have reduced manual reconciliation effort by up to 95%, significantly improving audit readiness and month-end close efficiency. I am proficient in Oracle NetSuite, Coupa, SAP S/4HANA, Tally ERP, Advanced Excel, Power BI, and AI-assisted validation workflows.</p>
    </div>
